Package com.tractrac.model.lib.api.event

Interface IEvent

All Superinterfaces:
IAttachable, IIdentifiable, INamed
public interface IEvent extends INamed
Encapsulates data related to an Event: Races, Competitors, Competitor Classes, Routes.
Author:
Jesper Grooss
